      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Muhammad Bin Yahya, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad Bin Isa, from Usman Bin Isa, form Sama’at, ",
          "Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘For everything there is a Limit (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>), and the one who exceeds that Limit (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>), there would be a Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">punishment</span>) upon him’."
